  "prompt": "What is a suitable solar panel installation provider near Somis, California CA?",
  "response": "When looking for a suitable solar panel installation provider near Somis, California, it's important to consider factors such as experience, customer reviews, certifications, and the range of services offered. Here are a few reputable providers that serve the Somis area:\n\n### 1. **SunPower by Stellar Solar**\n   - **Location:** Based in San Diego, but serves the entire state of California, including Somis.\n   - **Overview:** SunPower is known for its high-efficiency solar panels and comprehensive service offerings. They provide custom solar solutions, including installation, maintenance, and monitoring.\n   - **Website:** [SunPower by Stellar Solar](https://www.stellarsolar.net/)\n\n### 2. **Guzman Energy Group**\n   - **Location:** Based in Oxnard, CA, serving Somis and the surrounding areas.\n   - **Overview:** Guzman Energy Group specializes in residential and commercial solar installations. They offer a variety of solar products and services, including battery storage options.\n   - **Website:** [Guzman Energy Group](https://www.guzmanenergy.com/)\n\n### 3. **SolarMax Technology**\n   - **Location:** Based in Riverside, CA, with services extending to Somis.\n   - **Overview:** SolarMax Technology offers a wide range of solar solutions, including installation, financing options, and maintenance. They have a strong reputation for customer service and quality installations.\n   - **Website:** [SolarMax Technology](https://www.solarmax.com/)\n\n### 4. **Eco Solar Solutions**\n   - **Location:** Based in Moorpark, CA, serving Somis and nearby communities.\n   - **Overview:** Eco Solar Solutions provides customized solar energy systems for residential and commercial properties. They focus on delivering energy-efficient solutions tailored to individual needs.\n   - **Website:** [Eco Solar Solutions](https://www.ecosolarsolutions.com/)\n\n### 5. **Vivint Solar**\n   - **Location:** Nationwide provider with services available in Somis, CA.\n   - **Overview:** Vivint Solar offers solar panel installation, financing options, and energy monitoring services. They are known for their lease and power purchase agreement (PPA) options.\n   - **Website:** [Vivint Solar](https://www.vivintsolar.com/)\n\n### How to Choose the Best Provider:\n- **Compare Quotes:** Obtain quotes from multiple providers to compare pricing and services.\n- **Check Reviews:** Look at customer reviews and ratings on platforms like Yelp, Google, and the Better Business Bureau (BBB).\n- **Certifications:** Ensure the provider is licensed and certified by relevant authorities, such as NABCEP (North American Board of Certified Energy Practitioners).\n- **Warranty and Maintenance:** Inquire about the warranty on both the panels and the installation work, as well as the maintenance services offered.\n\nBy considering these factors, you can select a provider that best meets your energy needs and budget.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
